          piace sperimentare nuovi strumenti e linguaggi di programmazione.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Esperienze professionali</h3>

        <div class="flex">
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center mr-4">
            <div class="dark:bg-green-300 bg-green-500 rounded-full h-4 w-4">
            </div>
            <div
              class="dark:bg-green-300 bg-green-500 rounded-full flex-1 h-full w-1 -mt-1"
            >
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">
              Realizzazione Siti Business &bull; 2019 - 2023
